{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Grab your pickle guns, climb on top of your candy-vacuuming, self-driving chariot, and clean the village of the candy-stealing naughty mobs who have taken control! Take back insane amounts of candy, duck the evil stuff those baddies throw at you, and battle your way to the final boss!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Candy Reclaim is your perfect family-friendly, decidedly non-scary, wacky party game. For this Halloween, it is full of pumpkins, ghosts, skeletons, and candy, challenging, and just plain fun!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Levels, Difficulties, Points</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle your way through seven levels in five difficulty settings. Collect candy for points and eat it for refilling your health, and build up a shield. But don't trigger a sugar overload - sugar is bad for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will also be rated on accuracy as well as how much candy you manage to eat during each level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Create local profiles for everyone for a friendly competition! Who scores the most?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">How To Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play seated or standing - you'll use your controllers to shoot as well as eat the candy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game auto-adjusts to any height of the player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Five difficulty levels ranging from Piece-Of-Cake (no damage!) to Frustrating (lots of damage!) mean everyone can play, and finish (!), this game. </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298540/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736930393","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298540/page.bg.jpg?t=1736930393","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298540/a8990c13091ce40f4b66b7ce2c79047b9343eeaa/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736930393","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamsta